    {"id":"principles-t","type":"text","x":390,"y":800,"width":460,"height":140,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":251,"version":1,"versionNonce":1,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"text":"Non-negotiable principles (AGENTS.md §3–§5)\n\n1. Cosmos-first writes (truth before cache)\n2. Cache misses are normal — Redis down ⇒ slower, not broken\n3. TTL everything in Redis\n4. Classifier queue: AOF + Cosmos-pending-first + janitor sweep\n5. Never delete — curator only archives. Pinned skills immune.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":"principles","originalText":"Non-negotiable principles (AGENTS.md §3–§5)\n\n1. Cosmos-first writes (truth before cache)\n2. Cache misses are normal — Redis down ⇒ slower, not broken\n3. TTL everything in Redis\n4. Classifier queue: AOF + Cosmos-pending-first + janitor sweep\n5. Never delete — curator only archives. Pinned skills immune.","lineHeight":1.25},

