    {"id":"legend","type":"rectangle","x":40,"y":1000,"width":1260,"height":140,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#ffffff","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"dashed","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":600,"version":1,"versionNonce":1,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"legend-t"}],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"id":"legend-t","type":"text","x":60,"y":1015,"width":1220,"height":110,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":601,"version":1,"versionNonce":1,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"text":"Legend — arrow colours encode data direction:\n• Cyan (Cosmos)  — truth writes, Cosmos-first.        • Red (Redis) — cache + locks + queue coordination.        • Green (Blob) — immutable bytes; user-delegation SAS.\n• Orange — worker actions (Classifier / Curator).        • Purple — Foundry LLM (M3 review).        • Blue dotted — Entra ID identity (OIDC JWT for humans, MSI for app).\n• Red labelled (1)(2)(3) — consumer-agent download path: API auth, signed SAS redirect, then direct Blob GET. Bytes never proxy through FastAPI.\nLocal dev: docker-compose runs Cosmos emulator + Azurite + Redis 7 (zero Azure spend). Production: passwordless via DefaultAzureCredential + RBAC.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":"legend","originalText":"Legend — arrow colours encode data direction:\n• Cyan (Cosmos)  — truth writes, Cosmos-first.        • Red (Redis) — cache + locks + queue coordination.        • Green (Blob) — immutable bytes; user-delegation SAS.\n• Orange — worker actions (Classifier / Curator).        • Purple — Foundry LLM (M3 review).        • Blue dotted — Entra ID identity (OIDC JWT for humans, MSI for app).\n• Red labelled (1)(2)(3) — consumer-agent download path: API auth, signed SAS redirect, then direct Blob GET. Bytes never proxy through FastAPI.\nLocal dev: docker-compose runs Cosmos emulator + Azurite + Redis 7 (zero Azure spend). Production: passwordless via DefaultAzureCredential + RBAC.","lineHeight":1.25}
